CommandFileWatcher.CommandFile

CommandFileWatcher.CommandFile (File cmdFile, 
                List<String> extraArgs, 
                List<File> dependencies)

Construct a CommandFile

Parameters
cmdFile File: a File representing the command file path
extraArgs List: A List of extra arguments that should be used when the command is rerun.
dependencies List: The command files that this command file requires as transitive dependencies. A change in any of the dependencies will trigger a reload, but none of the dependencies themselves will be reloaded directly, only the main command file, cmdFile.
